Package: obr
Title: Access Office for Budget Responsibility Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Coverdale", email = "charlesfcoverdale@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides clean, tidy access to data published by the Office for
    Budget Responsibility (OBR), the UK's independent fiscal watchdog. Includes
    the Public Finances Databank (monthly outturn for PSNB, PSND, receipts, and
    expenditure) and the Historical Official Forecasts Database (OBR forecasts
    vs outturn at each fiscal event since 2010). Data is downloaded from the OBR
    on first use and cached locally for subsequent calls.
